<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-light">
  <div class="container px-4 mx-auto">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-12 lg:flex-row">
      <!-- Text Content -->
      <div class="lg:w-1/2 animate-slide-up">
        <h2 class="mb-6 font-serif text-3xl font-medium md:text-4xl">
          Our Story
        </h2>
        <div class="w-20 h-1 mb-8 bg-secondary"></div>
        <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          Located on Yarm High Street, La Piazza is a new fine dining restaurant offering a unique culinary experience. Our journey began in 2025 with a simple vision: to create a place where exceptional food, creative cocktails, and elegant ambiance come together.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          Chef Michael Thompson, with his 20 years of culinary expertise, leads our kitchen team in creating dishes that blend traditional techniques with modern innovation. We source only the finest seasonal ingredients from local suppliers, ensuring that every plate served is of the highest quality.
        </p>
        <a href="/about" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 text-white transition-colors rounded-sm bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark">
          Learn More About Us
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Image Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 lg:w-1/2 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
        <img
          src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/262978/pexels-photo-262978.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=2"
          alt="Restaurant interior"
          class="object-cover w-full h-64 rounded"
        />
        <img
          src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/370984/pexels-photo-370984.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=2"
          alt="Gourmet dish"
          class="object-cover w-full h-64 rounded"
        />
        <img
          src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/2122294/pexels-photo-2122294.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=2"
          alt="Chef preparing food"
          class="object-cover w-full h-64 rounded"
        />
        <img
          src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/67468/pexels-photo-67468.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=2"
          alt="Cocktail drink"
          class="object-cover w-full h-64 rounded"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>